mean

Source: R/tensor.R
mean.tensor.Rd

mean

# S3 method for tensor
mean(x, dim = NULL, keepdim = NULL, dtype = NULL,
  na.rm = FALSE)

Arguments

x

tensor object
dim

dimension in which to sum
keepdim

wether to keep or not the dim
dtype

optionaly cast the sum result

Examples

x <- tensor(1:10)
mean(x)
